{"tid":1148094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳直升機墜灣仔維港　大批拯救人員趕往搜索","createTime":"2019-05-10T08:56:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-10T09:05:35.000Z","uid":6647,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c93c94e2be9aee626f3dfc5dda1927e74730db59","tid":1148094,"uid":6647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T08:56:50.000Z","msg":"今日（10日）下午3時許，警方接獲巿民報案，指一架直升機懷疑在灣仔會展對開失事墜海。目前大批拯救人員包括消防員前往現場搜索，並進一步了解事件。 <br />\n<br />\n運輸署宣佈，因突發事件，博覽道東近金紫荊廣場的唯一行車線現已封閉。現時上址交通繁忙。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53f6bd30bd887bddbd6c21cc93f74ccb7fc8a882","tid":1148094,"uid":6647,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T08:57:42.000Z","msg":"堅定流"},{"pid":"d6d26e2b9c4090be99fbfd9b881dc8da0630e41a","tid":1148094,"uid":113922,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T08:59:00.000Z","msg":"LINK又唔貼<br />\n自己問番堅定流<br />\n想點"},{"pid":"b2526439399d38d2b18e7bd92f1e148225e8f834","tid":1148094,"uid":19712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T09:00:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190510/bkn-20190510160756911-0510_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190510%2Fbkn-20190510160756911-0510_00822_001.html&d=hvrwae4HshPHSMms9GCCYF3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=78ae1fcd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190510/bkn-20190510160756911-0510_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"b8f5e19d4ca93da7ba64d4ff402cb44630e8db4e","tid":1148094,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T09:02:05.000Z","msg":"打飛機笑話弄假成真<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" cl